name: aws-license-manager-license-consumption-sample
description: AWS License Manager is a service that makes it easier for you to manage your software licenses from software vendors (such as Microsoft, SAP, Oracle, and IBM) centrally across AWS and your on-premises environments. This provides control and visibility into the usage of your licenses, and enables to limit licensing overages and reduce the risk of non-compliance or misreporting.
author: lxiangyiamazon
